text: Tarcoola is the name of a number of places in Australia: * Tarcoola, South Australia, a locality ** Tarcoola railway station, South Australia ** Tarcoola Airport ==Other uses== * Tarcoola (horse), the racehorse that won the 1893 Melbourne Cup horse race - refer List of Melbourne Cup winners ==See also== * Mount Tarcoola, Western Australia, a mountain * Tarcoola Beach, Western Australia, a locality
title: Tarcoola
